nano shortcuts :
1) Save : Ctrl + O
2) Exit : Ctrl + X
3) Copy : Alt+Shift+A or Ctrl+6 to set or unset mark.
          Use arrow keys to set highlight/select the text to be copied.
          Alt+Shift+6 or Alt+6 to copy.
4) Paste : Ctrl+U
5) Cut   : Ctrl+K
6) Show line numbers on left : Alt+Shift+3
7) Go to first line  : Alt+\
8) Go to last  line  : Alt+/
9) Go to line number, column number : Ctrl+_   <=underscore means Shift+(minus symbol)
10) Search and replace :
11)  Help : Ctrl+G

